Dec 20, 2025
Release Notes
Renders daily EMA, 10, 20 and 50 on any timeframe below 1D. Wont work below 5min.
Best results are when used at 30m, 2H or 4H timeframe.
Upward and downward trend are identified with:
10 > 20 + price > 50 for long and
10 < 20 + price < 50 for shorts or exits

This strategy is open-source use and meant as a starting point to build a more complex strategy.
It can be combined with other indicators to make a plan and backtest it.
